OL,3,CDoctors to be balloted on industrial
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,FHospital doctors in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fare to be balloted on industrial
OL,8,Faction, the British Medical
OL,9,FAssociation (BMA) has announced.
OL,11,FThe BMA said a recommendation from the
OL,12,FDoctors and Dentists Pay Review Body
OL,13,F(DDRB) of a 3.5% pay increase for
OL,14,Fdoctors in 2026/27 had been rejected
OL,15,Fas "unacceptable".
OL,17,FThe ballot will open on May 11 for
OL,18,Ffour weeks.
OL,26,@wD@DOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
