OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776780668
OL,3,CDoctors to be balloted on industrial
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,FThe BMA said members being balloted
OL,7,Finclude consultants, specialist,
OL,8,Fassociate specialist and specialty
OL,9,F(SAS) doctors and resident doctors.
OL,11,FDr David Farren, chairman of the
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland consultants
OL,13,Fcommittee, said: "We had hoped this
OL,14,Fyear's DDRB recommendation would be
OL,15,Fhigher, sending a clear message that
OL,16,Fthe work we do is valued and respected.
OL,18,F"The pressures on our members are
OL,19,Fgrowing day by day, but this uplift
OL,20,Fdoes not reflect the increasing
OL,21,Fcomplexity and challenge of the work.
OL,26,@uD@ROUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776780668
OL,3,CDoctors to be balloted on industrial
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,F"There is a real risk we will lose
OL,7,Fmore consultants through early
OL,8,Fretirement, reduced hours, or by
OL,9,Fleaving for better pay and a more
OL,10,Ffunctional health system elsewhere."
OL,12,FHe added: "We will now ballot
OL,13,Fconsultants with a view to taking
OL,14,Findustrial action.
OL,16,F"Unless urgent action is taken to fix
OL,17,Four pay, we will continue to lose
OL,18,Fdoctors from our health service and
OL,19,Fthe system will not be able to care
OL,20,Ffor patients."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]tD@KOUxD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
