OL,3,CDoctors to be balloted on industrial
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,FDr Leanne Davison, NISAS committee
OL,7,Fchairwoman, said: "SAS doctors are an
OL,8,Fessential part of the hospital
OL,9,Fworkforce, providing stability,
OL,10,Fexperience and continuity of care, yet
OL,11,Four contribution is consistently
OL,12,Fundervalued.
OL,14,F"Like our colleagues, we have seen our
OL,15,Fpay steadily eroded, making
OL,16,Frecruitment and retention increasingly
OL,17,Fdifficult.
OL,19,F"We have been left with no confidence
OL,20,Fthat these issues will be addressed
OL,21,Fthrough the usual channels.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
