OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776780668
OL,3,CDoctors to be balloted on industrial
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,F"Balloting for industrial action is
OL,7,Fabout standing up for fairness and for
OL,8,Fthe future of the health service in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,F"Without urgent action on pay, the
OL,12,Fsystem risks losing more skilled
OL,13,Fdoctors it simply cannot afford to
OL,14,Flose."
